      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated Double VANOS system. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its signature balance with a focused MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent service highlights include a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the high-revving 8,000 RPM valvetrain operates with peak mechanical integrity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this driver-focused example offers exceptional turn-in response and the unmistakable metallic rasp of a true M-engineered thoroughbred.",
